summary: I’ve been away and come back to Taylor singing Treacherous plus WIldest Dreams - two in my top 10. Plus Haunted from a few...
body: I’ve been away and come back to Taylor singing Treacherous plus WIldest Dreams - two in my top 10. Plus Haunted from a few nights ago. I can’t wait for November!!!! @taylorswift please don’t cut the setlist or stage for us Aussies, but if you need to I understand. Maybe you can play for me Wonderland or Tied Together with a Smile…. Girl can dream. But I’m just so excited and incredibly grateful to get to see you again   💋

It would be cool if I could have her write it out for me one day, but who knows if that will ever happen.
